<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Booking - Lisbon Hostel Booking</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f9fafb; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0da2ff 0%, #0088e6 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 40px 30px; color: #111827; }
    .booking-details { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .guest-info { border-left: 4px solid #2cb1a6; padding-left: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .property-info { border-left: 4px solid #f8e6a0; padding-left: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background-color: #0088e6; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px; }
    .highlight { color: #0088e6; font-weight: 600; }
    .success { color: #2cb1a6; }
    .warning { color: #ff8212; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üéâ New Booking Confirmed!</h1>
      <p>Lisbon Hostel Booking</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{hostName}},</p>

      <p>Great news! You have a new confirmed booking at <strong>{{propertyName}}</strong>.</p>

      <div class="booking-details">
        <h3>üìÖ Booking Details</h3>
        <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> {{bookingId}}</p>
        <p><strong>Check-in:</strong> {{checkInDate}} at {{checkInTime}}</p>
        <p><strong>Check-out:</strong> {{checkOutDate}} at {{checkOutTime}}</p>
        <p><strong>Guests:</strong> {{guestCount}}</p>
        <p><strong>Total Amount:</strong> <span class="highlight">‚Ç¨{{totalAmount}}</span></p>
        <p><strong>Payment Status:</strong> <span class="success">‚úÖ Paid</span></p>
      </div>

      <div class="guest-info">
        <h3>üë§ Guest Information</h3>
        <p><strong>{{guestName}}</strong></p>
        <p>Email: {{guestEmail}}</p>
        {{#if guestPhone}}<p>Phone: {{guestPhone}}</p>{{/if}}
      </div>

      <div class="property-info">
        <h3>üè® Property Details</h3>
        <p><strong>{{propertyName}}</strong></p>
        <p>{{propertyAddress}}</p>
      </div>

      {{#if specialRequests}}
      <div class="booking-details">
        <h3>üìù Special Requests</h3>
        <p class="warning">{{specialRequests}}</p>
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Review the booking details and guest information</li>
        <li>Contact the guest if you have any questions</li>
        <li>Prepare the room for check-in</li>
        <li>Send welcome instructions to the guest</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="{{bookingManagementUrl}}" class="cta-button">Manage This Booking</a>
      </div>

      <p>Thank you for being part of the Lisbon Hostel Booking community!</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>
      <span style="color: #f8e6a0;">The Lisbon Hostel Booking Team</span></p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p><strong>Lisbon Hostel Booking</strong></p>
      <p>Fair, local, hostel-first bookings in Lisbon ‚Äî no hidden fees.</p>
      <p>Questions? Contact us at support@lisbonhostelbooking.com</p>
      <p>&copy; 2025 Lisbon Hostel Booking. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>